div.div: Hello there, thanks for reporting. Just wondering, did you try scrolling horizontally with shift+scrollwheel ?

Better Radar and improved ATIS


Additions
* The "status" field of a strip is now managed by cycling through statuses with "Q" and "E"
* Added relevant waypoints to the radar screen for all major airports
* Aircraft wake categories (if included in callsign) will now be replaced with their identifier
e.g. "Heavy" -> /H, "Super" -> /J
* Added an "Additional NOTAMs" area to the ATIS generator to allow aerodrome-specific notams.

Fixes
* The ATIS identifier is now always capitalized in a generated ATIS
* Improved Radar screen performance

Happy Controlling
- Zedruc
